infographic sequence-steps-badge-card
data
  title Target-host deploy loop
  desc Local preview, remote execution, and fetched evidence stay inside one operator flow.
  sequences
    - label package
      desc ran.package_bootstrap
    - label preview
      desc ran-install or Deploy Studio
    - label ship
      desc bundle plus rendered files
    - label preflight
      desc host probe and readiness
    - label remote ranctl
      desc plan, apply, verify
    - label fetchback
      desc remote runs and debug packs
  order asc
theme
  palette #92400e #d97706 #0f766e #1d4ed8 #334155 #7c2d12
  base
    text
      font-family Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui
